      "text": "PAYMENT SERVICE\n\nPayment: \nNot needed for v1; \nuse inquiry-first sales.\n\nFuture payment option:\n* Vipps ePayment later\nif direct checkout\nbecomes necessary.\n* Stripe if internation\ncard payments become\nimportant",
